videos.description: After grabbing the offensive rebound off Tennessee's Jaime Nared's missed shot, Mercedes Russell backs down a defender and converts the layup.
videos.headline: Russell converts second-chance bucket

videos.description: After getting the steal, Tennessee's Jaime Nared goes coast-to-coast and converts the tough and-1 lay-in.
videos.headline: Nared sinks tough layup for 3-point chance

videos.description: Notre Dame's Jessica Shepard send a pass up court to Marina Mabrey for the tough layup, earning a trip to the line for a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Shepard's long pass sets up Mabrey's and-1 layup

videos.description: Notre Dame's Marina Mabrey tries going up for the layup but is rejected by Tennessee's Evina Westbrook in the second quarter.
videos.headline: Westbrook denies Mabrey's lay-in

videos.description: Notre Dame's Jessica Shepard finds Jackie Young cutting down the lane for the finger roll lay-in.
videos.headline: Shepard sets up Young's finger roll

videos.description: Tennessee's Evina Westbrook pulls up behind the arc and knocks down the 3-pointer to end the third quarter.
videos.headline: Westbrook beats the buzzer on 3 ball

videos.description: Notre Dame's Jessica Shepard leads Kathryn Westbeld to the basket for the tough layup and the 3-point opportunity.
videos.headline: Shepard's dime sets up Westbeld's tough lay-in

videos.description: Notre Dame's Arike Ogunbowale tries going up with a layup but is denied by Tennessee's Evina Westbrook in the fourth quarter.
videos.headline: Westbrook swats Ogunbowale's layup

videos.description: Trailing by 23 points in the second quarter, No. 5 Notre Dame makes a furious comeback to beat No. 6 Tennessee 84-70.
videos.headline: Notre Dame overcomes 23-point deficit to beat Tennessee
